Detail Design

  • Detail drawings for manufacturing
  • Rendering for presentations, catalogues

Industry Domains

  • Industrial Automation
  • Water Treatment
  • Oil & Gas
  • Engineering and Construction
  • Packaging

Computer Aided Design

  • SolidWorks
